executor_description: Checks the status of a TM import.
Generates the key associated with a username.
Contributes a translation unit (segment and translation) in some language pair to MyMemory. Without specifying any key parameter, the contribution is available for everybody (Thank you!).

Contributes a whole translation memory (in TMX format) to MyMemory. It accepts multi-language memories and it autodetects languages from internal meta-information. Without specifying any key parameter, the contribution is available for everybody (Thank you!).
Searches MyMemory for matches against a segment.
List available subjects in MyMemory for querying and TM importing.
